graph TD
    Precipitation[Precipitation Sensor] -->|Rain percentage| Monitor[WeatherMonitor class]
    Monitor -->|Rain >= 80%| Failsafe[Failsafe Triggered]
    
    Battery[Battery Telemetry] -->|Voltage/Percentage| BatEngine[BatteryManager class]
    BatEngine -->|Percentage <= 20%| Failsafe
    
    Failsafe --> Locate[EmergencyLandingPlanner class]
    Locate -->|Search coordinates| HubDB[( designated landing hubs )]
    HubDB -->|Closest hub coordinates| Target[Landing Target Locked]
    
    Target --> Override[Autopilot override steer RTL]
    Override --> Descent[Safe Autonomous Landing]
